title: Ep 333 | Jase's Dramatic Fight Embarrasses Missy in Front of Guests, and Did Judas Have Free Will?
description:
Jase unintentionally embarrasses Missy in front of company, and then he scares her half to death. Al talks about his vendetta against wasps. Phil and Jase recap Romans 16. The guys talk about why Judas made his choices and whether or not free will was involved. And Jase explains that when God comes calling, there's only question: Will you answer?
